Ken Programming Language
========================

Ken transpile to portable C11 code. The transpiler is written in C and is currently in early development. Do not use this in production.

The purpose of creating Ken is to code simple but fast like C & Safe like rust (probably).

example code
------------

Hello world:
  func main() -> void {
      let a = "Hello, World!";
      println!(a);
  }

String Interpolation:
  func greet(name: str) -> void {
      println!("Hello {name}!");
  }

Status
======

Work in progress. Things will break.
